15
00:00:35,119 --> 00:00:38,239
from fake smiles better than humans can.

16
00:00:38,239 --> 00:00:40,799
Before we get into that, though, a question.

17
00:00:40,799 --> 00:00:44,799
The expressions that we can make with our face are controlled by muscles.

18
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:47,359
How many muscles do we have in our face?

19
00:00:47,359 --> 00:00:52,239
Is it a 26, b 43 or c 62?

20
00:00:52,239 --> 00:00:53,599
What do you think, Sam?

21
00:00:53,599 --> 00:00:56,480
No idea, but a lot, I'd guess.

22
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:58,480
So I'm going with 62.

23
00:00:58,559 --> 00:01:00,879
OK, well, we'll see if you'll be smiling

24
