through obviously computer through video frames

71
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:06,879
and trying to understand how these muscle movements

72
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:09,599
actually relate to facial expressions

73
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:11,199
and then from facial expressions

74
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,799
trying to understand the emotions

75
