100
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:25,360
This means that they make the smiles come naturally.

101
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:29,520
They assume that the smiles while watching the funny films are genuine.

102
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:32,000
And then they ask the people to pretend to smile

103
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:36,000
