116
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:11,760
Sadly, you are not using different muscles for that sort of sad look.

117
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,640
Actually, the answer is 43.

118
00:05:14,719 --> 00:05:17,199
Congratulations to anyone who got that right.

119
